LAHORE, Jul 01 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has felicitated the Chinese government, leadership and its people on the 100th anniversary of the establishment of Chinese Communist Party (CCP).
In his message on Thursday, the chief minister expressed his good wishes to the president, prime minister, ambassador and other officials of China on the occasion of the 100th anniversary of the CCP.
